<node id="World Athletics Federation">
  <data key="d0">World Athletics Federation</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d0d3b88d3601a1081c8354e0ef27952f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39206ec5906f23d68e051b1df74d3ca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab226f704fc1b4d45dd06222f40cb39f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c4967b23b72f04d5c4ef37149d21ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75fa98905e1d68515f390e75c46adddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-412e17859c430b9ce8b929bc152053ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bddb98b4a84e394c0a4558b42ae12d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c7743e93210e95e8e40e0d2a627684b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-07959bdb8bab221c9c80a1c3e85776b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25d7c29d65aa0e4d54fb4af54207fa0d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41be59e9bae9e87a716afd8b5a9e9ee1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dddcb833d814b293bd936732652206d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76068a2f95fd89e7ceb4741d4eb478ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84c3e0271089b72556be831ea38a055f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f0773b8daffa7a65254a73867e36afb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-082efb5c18d778427dcd94905e5f4370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17b29d261b8bce3ef9105d1c8a78415d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f23819b8640c43571e6e9b3e4098e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2fe3f974e54dd1f1ad98289cc79980d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0640212d45b4b92d91d0255cf90edf96&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0c6684aa00106f16e7869f519061642&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0cef05272158ef916c2b84f625b2ddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f6caccf00501b5f4caf06dcfc047ae9e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2a0171ee9d19cc664d4d041d3e73ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6e1908b68b82814f06780675f7938b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5096c0cdf6972a3670732e4f9be1d36a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d02e98febcd8f8650bbe77d789a41d69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cafeb58d25cc4cbc85eaf07cf415496a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4861ed7c0c566a81f361adb6811a1523&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-886b4b629f3088ef8656c792cf7b3e8b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-345e520afd2a192e25824abb33740d46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b9e37e8f7e8a98183b1724c16ce814a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c1fca5402ff2eb1c53222e1d4db282a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-490df5a6810de4f040c4fe2681e6ed6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe7268a7cb94439d483759e501068db6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5930b403906ecb929487592cef5210f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a83bcdf6e7b7269cfd17b4f21457de8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-67cc5a5ed7a1cbea5f9e6d5f5d08ab51&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6f1e5469f6278ea8a34bff96b293b69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a40e782f3c3804da0a1d45dfa05eefe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0cd3e323fc2a43e461d7af757b08706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-996c8aba3ce4de0e9bb90c0d569231f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8ec2739edb4ee1ccc4cf68534e90be5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9648988cb67db9843bc13754ac3d6ab6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c41e50d3a458388dc7fe53ece68ee69f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6839b81653aa7c9b7ec794f3447380&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fcc4bf66788ce00c23c3e736753ea50a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-068ca517cbebf973fd4089bd45ef615c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0add79f46581b83deba682a2c89cdb7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5618eb566fb322ada0eb69bef88a7581</data>
  <data key="d2">World Athletics Federation is responsible for overseeing global athletics competitions, including prestigious events such as the World Athletics Championships. The federation plays a crucial role in validating world records set by athletes during these competitions and other athletic events worldwide. Its primary responsibilities include ensuring that all records meet stringent criteria and standards to be officially recognized, thereby contributing significantly to maintaining high performance benchmarks and upholding the integrity and credibility of achievements within the international athletics community.

World Athletics Federation oversees not only the World Athletics Championships but also numerous other global athletic events. The federation's duties encompass validating athletic records set by athletes in these competitions, ensuring compliance with established criteria that maintain fairness and excellence across the sport. This validation process is essential for confirming the legitimacy of world records, thereby upholding the reputation of athletics globally.

In summary, World Athletics Federation oversees a comprehensive range of global athletic events and record validations, contributing to the integrity and credibility of achievements in international competitions like the World Athletics Championships. Its role extends to validating records set by athletes across various competitions to ensure high performance benchmarks are maintained within the sport.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation oversees the World Athletics Championship and validates athletic records.</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
