<node id="B人員">
  <data key="d0">B人員</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">B人員 is an engineer with a broad range of responsibilities related to system and record maintenance. Specifically, B人员 oversees the maintenance of systems for clients such as C客户 and D客戶. This includes maintaining the Splunk system for D客户 and managing maintenance records for both C客户 and Cお客様. B人员 performs various tasks to ensure that all necessary maintenance work is thoroughly documented and completed, indicating a comprehensive involvement in multiple aspects of maintenance activities on behalf of these clients.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is the engineer responsible for handling the maintenance work.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is the engineer responsible for handling the maintenance service.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is the engineer responsible for handling the maintenance work.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is the engineer responsible for handling the maintenance tasks.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is an engineer responsible for handling the maintenance of C客户的systems.</data>
