<node id="E客戶">
  <data key="d0">E客戶</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">E客戶 is an organization that receives maintenance services, particularly related to Splunk systems. Maintenance activities conducted on behalf of E客戶 are meticulously documented in detailed maintenance records. These records track various work items and on-site activities performed by personnel such as C人员. The comprehensive history provided by these records supports ongoing service and support needs for the organization.

E 고객은 Splunk 시스템의 유지보수를 받는 조직으로, 이에 대한 다양한 유지보수 활동이 문서화됩니다. 이러한 유지보수 기록들은 E 고객의 전체 유지보수 작업을 철저하게 추적하며, 이를 통해 지속적인 서비스 및 지원 요구를 효과적으로 관리합니다.

E客戶是接受Splunk系统维护服务的客户组织，其维护活动被详细记录在案。这些维护记录涵盖了在现场进行的各种工作项目，并由相关工作人员如C人员执行和文档化。这些详尽的历史记录支持该组织持续的服务和支持需求。

Given that the descriptions are consistent and do not indicate any conflicting entities, the summary integrates all provided information seamlessly.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶is an organization for which maintenance records are kept.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶is a customer entity for whom maintenance records are kept.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶is a customer for whom maintenance records are kept.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶is a client organization for which maintenance records are kept.</data>
