<node id="Splunk每週onsite">
  <data key="d0">Splunk每週onsite</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">**Splunk每週onsite** is a term that describes the regular, weekly on-site work conducted by engineers at B客戶's site. This activity encompasses various maintenance tasks and activities aimed at ensuring the proper functioning of Splunk systems. The primary purpose of Splunk每週onsite is to perform ongoing maintenance for B客戶, including necessary system checks and updates carried out by Splunk engineers. These weekly visits involve a range of duties that are critical for maintaining the health and performance of the installed Splunk systems.&lt;SEP&gt;#Splunk每週onsite refers to a weekly on-site service for B客戶using Splunk software.&lt;SEP&gt;Splunk每週onsite refers to regular on-site maintenance work conducted for Splunk systems.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773781631</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="A部門">
  <data key="d0">A部門</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">A部門 is an unspecified department within an organization, primarily responsible for conducting various maintenance activities. It plays a crucial role in multiple aspects of the maintenance process and performs specific actions during this period. A部門 oversees tasks such as Splunk role capability anomalies, PA monthly report trigger changes, and Linux host user management. Additionally, it conducts account inventory checks and is involved in adjusting Splunk user permissions.

A部門 operates within B客戶, where various maintenance tasks are performed, indicating its involvement in broader organizational processes beyond a single context. It handles the responsibilities related to maintaining system integrity and operational efficiency, contributing significantly to the overall performance of the organization's IT infrastructure.&lt;SEP&gt;A部門is a department involved in the maintenance tasks related to PA report and other issues.&lt;SEP&gt;A部門is an organizational unit where certain Splunk maintenance tasks were carried out.&lt;SEP&gt;A部門is a department within B客戶's organization that deals with multiple technical tasks.&lt;SEP&gt;A部門is a department involved in the maintenance of Splunk systems and services.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773781631</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="B部門">
  <data key="d0">B部門</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">B部門 is a department within the organization that requires maintenance services and performs several critical tasks. It is involved in FISAC data containment, retention, and intake, as well as SH KVstore engine anomaly testing. The department also handles troubleshooting of n8n connectivity issues to Splunk and conducts KV store certificate updates. Additionally, B部門 manages Splunk bundle storage optimization and monitors the synchronization status checks for indexer indexes.

B部門 plays a crucial role in maintaining the integrity and functionality of these systems by addressing specific maintenance needs related to Splunk and indexing systems. The department's responsibilities include ensuring data security through FISAC data containment and retention processes, conducting thorough testing on SH KVstore engines to identify and resolve anomalies, and optimizing storage solutions for efficient operation.

Overall, B部門 is an integral part of the organization that focuses on a range of maintenance activities essential for system reliability and performance.&lt;SEP&gt;B部門is another department within B客戶's organization, involved in specific technical tasks like FISAC data retention and SH KVstore engine anomaly testing.&lt;SEP&gt;B部門is another department involved in specific tasks such as setting up FIsac情报提取and adding indexers to the IDX cluster.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773781631</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
