<edge source="B客戶" target="C人員">
  <data key="d7">13.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(B客戶, C人員) refers to a relationship where C人員 provides various maintenance services to B klientów during specified time periods. This includes handling tasks related to hard drive space and data synchronization issues. C人員 is consistently engaged in the maintenance process for B клиент, conducting necessary maintenance activities as required. The descriptions indicate that C人员 also participates in the maintenance work for B客户, addressing specific technological concerns such as data management issues. Overall, C人员 is deeply involved in ensuring the smooth operation of B客户的 systems through regular and targeted maintenance efforts.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員also contributed to the maintenance tasks at B客戶's site on 2025/12/17.&lt;SEP&gt;#C人員also handles maintenance tasks for B客户提供维护。&lt;SEP&gt;Maintenance record for B客戶involves C personnel as well.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員also provides maintenance services to B客戶alongside A人員.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is also involved in providing maintenance support to B客戶.</data>
  <data key="d9">customer service,maintenance,maintenance record,maintenance support,record-keeping,responsibility,service delivery,service provider,service provision,support</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-d0d3b88d3601a1081c8354e0ef27952f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39206ec5906f23d68e051b1df74d3ca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84c3e0271089b72556be831ea38a055f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6e1908b68b82814f06780675f7938b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b</data>
