<edge source="B客戶" target="A人員">
  <data key="d7">13.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(A人员, B客户) refers to a relationship where A人员 provides various types of maintenance services for B客户. The descriptions indicate that A人员 is responsible for handling maintenance tasks and records related to B客户的 systems. This includes both ongoing service provision and specific instances where maintenance was carried out on particular dates.

A人员 regularly handles maintenance tasks such as addressing issues, updating system statuses, and ensuring the proper functioning of B客户的 systems. For example, on 2025/11/06 and 2025/12/17, A人员 provided specific maintenance services for B客户, reflecting a consistent pattern of service delivery over time.

The relationship encompasses not only reactive problem-solving but also proactive management to prevent system failures. This is evident from the descriptions that emphasize both ongoing support and detailed records of maintenance activities conducted by A人员 on behalf of B客户.&lt;SEP&gt;#A人員handles maintenance tasks for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;Maintenance record for B客戶is handled by A personnel.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員is providing maintenance services to B客戶as part of the recorded maintenance activities.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員provides maintenance and technical support for B客戶's systems.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員provides maintenance services for B客戶.</data>
