<edge source="C人員" target="E客戶">
  <data key="d7">16.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(C人員, E客戶) refers to a relationship where C人員 provides comprehensive maintenance and support services specifically tailored to meet the needs of E客戶. This relationship involves both proactive and reactive measures aimed at ensuring the smooth operation and optimal functionality of critical systems managed by E客户, particularly focusing on the Splunk system.

C人員 is responsible for various forms of maintenance activities that are carried out either remotely or directly on-site at E客户的 facilities. These tasks include handling the maintenance records and conducting maintenance operations as described in status updates and other relevant documentation. The relationship emphasizes a formal arrangement where C人员 offers continuous support to maintain the integrity and reliability of systems under E客戶's management.

E客户 engages with C人員 explicitly for these services, underscoring the importance of this support role in ensuring that critical technological infrastructure remains operational and efficient. This interaction highlights a structured approach where both parties collaborate closely to address maintenance needs promptly and effectively.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員provided maintenance services for E客戶during the specified time period.</data>
  <data key="d9">client relationship,client service,client-engineer relationship,customer service,customer-engineer,maintenance,maintenance service,maintenance support,maintenance work,record keeper,responsibility,service,service delivery,service provision,technical assistance</data>
