<edge source="C客戶" target="B人員">
  <data key="d7">16.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(B人员, C客户) refers to a relationship where B人员 is responsible for providing comprehensive maintenance services and handling the maintenance tasks for C客户. This role includes maintaining detailed records of all activities related to the systems or accounts managed by C客户. Specifically, B人员 ensures that all necessary documentation and service work are completed to support the operational needs of C客户的 infrastructure or services effectively.

B人员 performs various duties such as system maintenance, record keeping, and ensuring the proper functioning of C客户的 infrastructure or services. This role involves both proactive measures to prevent issues before they arise and reactive solutions when problems occur, contributing to the overall reliability and stability of C客户’s systems under management. Additionally, B人员 provides specialized maintenance support for specific technologies such as Splunk SIEM, further enhancing the service provided to C客户.

In summary, (B人员, C客户) encompasses a wide range of responsibilities centered around ensuring that C客户的 systems operate smoothly and efficiently through continuous maintenance efforts and thorough documentation practices.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員performs maintenance tasks for C客戶as part of their responsibilities.</data>
